<td>2-5 business days</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Up to 3 Kg</td>\n      <td>12,00 €</td>\n      <td>2-5 business days</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Up to 5 Kg</td>\n      <td>16,00 €</td>\n      <td>2-5 business days</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Up to 10 Kg</td>\n      <td>19,00 €</td>\n      <td>2-5 business days</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n<p>Norway has a freight cost of 12.00€ (does not include customs clearance fees)</p>\n<p>Bosnia and Hezergova has a freight cost of 13€ (does not include customs clearance fees)</p>\n<p>Serbia has a freight cost of 13€ (does not include customs clearance fees)</p>\n<p></p>\n<h4>Spanish islands - Balearic Islands, Canary Islands, Ceuta and Melilla</h4>\n<table>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <th>Weight</th>\n      <th>Balearic Islands</th>\n      <th>Canary Islands</th>\n      <th>Ceuta and Melilla</th>\n      <th>\n        Days</th>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Up to 1 Kg</td>\n      <td>7,00 €</td>\n      <td>10,00 €</td>\n      <td>10,00 €</td>\n      <td>3 to 4 business days</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Up to 3 Kg</td>\n      <td>8,50 €</td>\n      <td>15,00 €</td>\n      <td>13,00 €</td>\n      <td>3 to 4 business days</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Up to 5 Kg</td>\n      <td>10,00 €</td>\n      <td>20,00 €</td>\n      <td>15,00 €</td>\n      <td>3 to 4 business days</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Up to 10 Kg</td>\n      <td>13,00 €</td>\n      <td>43,00 €</td>\n      <td>23,00 €</td>\n      <td>3 to 4 business days</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n<p>Commercial shipments <=15kg and with amount <=150,25€. Dispatch at destination: 13,99€.</p>\n<p>Commercial shipments >15kg and value > 150,25€. Dispatch at origin: 17,37€. Dispatch at destination: 26,31€.</p>\n<p>Ceuta/Melilla: Dispatch origin: 17,37€. Dispatch at destination: 26,31€.</p>"
